# Prompt Library for Educator-Focused LLM Tasks

This prompt library contains a curated set of high-quality prompts designed for K–12 educators.  
The collection highlights a range of instructional tasks including standards-aligned content creation, differentiation, misconception correction, multilingual supports, and project-based learning design.

These prompts demonstrate:
- Strong instructional design awareness  
- Alignment to K–12 teaching standards  
- Classroom-ready clarity  
- Support for diverse learners  
- Structured thinking for repeatable LLM workflows  

Use these prompts as-is or adapt them to match grade bands, content standards, or classroom needs
